	   <tr><td colspan=2>Ok, finally got a reply on another board so I will share the Info =)<br><br>Mistress Latazura<br>Level 63-65 about 100k+ hps<br>Quad's max hit is 375<br>She is a Siren Enchanter and is not slowable.<br>She spawns in the siren building with 3 bridges leading into it... fairly close to zoneline.<br><br>Drops:<br>Cloak of the Seacaller: AC: +10 Int: +8 All Resists +3&nbsp;&nbsp;Mana: +65 <br>Gloomwater Bow 25/55 4 to all resists procs 40% snare<br>Lyendlln's Lute 10ac 25hp bard insturment +30% lute songs<br>The Runed Sea Shell's for the 9th ring and 7th prayer shawl quests.<br>Sleeves of the Kelpmaidens 3ac 10str effect Enduring Breath <br><br>This information was kindly provided by Annihilus Maximus on the Saryrn Tavern boards.<br>&nbsp;<br>Baron Zendrak Advoco<br>Lvl 61 Arch Mage of Saryrn<br>Master of the Orb<br>Member of Familjen</td></tr>
